# This file is committed to the repo as a reference — do NOT put real secrets here.
# Copy this to .env.local and fill in the real key for local testing with `netlify dev`.
#
# Required for the AI Study Assistant (js/api.js -> netlify/functions/summarize.js):
#   GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
#
# Get a free key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#
# Set the REAL value in Netlify, not in this file:
#   Netlify dashboard > Site configuration > Environment variables > Add a variable
#   Key:   GEMINI_API_KEY
#   Value: <your real key>
#
# If you use `netlify dev` locally, create a *.env.local* file (already gitignored)
# with the real key so it's picked up automatically without ever being committed.
